<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>게시글 정보 확인 및 수정/삭제</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/article.css" />

</head>
<body>
    <h1>게시글 정보 확인 및 수정/삭제</h1>
    
    <form action="/articles/modify/<%=article.articleIDX %>" method="post">
        제목:<input type="text" name="title" value="<%=article.title %>"/> <br/>
        내용:<textarea name="contents" rows="20" cols="10" style="width:90%"><%=article.contents %></textarea><br/>
        등록자:<input type="text" name="register" value="<%=article.articleIDX %>"/> <br/>
        <a href="/articles/list">수정</a>
        <a href="/articles/delete/<%=article.articleIDX %>>">삭제</a>
        <a href="/articles/list">게시글 목록 이동</a>
    </form>

</body>
</html>